# Azerbaijani (North) → IPA transliteration rules (az_ipa.rules)
#
# Sources:
# - Mokari, P. G. & Werner, S. (2017). “Azerbaijani.” JIPA 47(2): 207–212.
# - Standard Baku-oriented descriptions of orthography & pronunciation (e.g. Siegel, Essentials of Azerbaijani).
#
# Simplified: no vowel length, no stress, no aspiration marking, no dental vs. alveolar
# distinctions, no automatic final devoicing, no systematic palatal/velar allophony.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# 0. MACROS  (IPA target symbols; used in contexts below)

$V   = [ i y e œ æ ɑ o u ɯ ];   # all vowels
$BV  = [ ɑ o u ɯ ];             # back vowels
$FV  = [ i y e œ æ ];           # front vowels
$RV  = [ o œ u y ];             # rounded vowels

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

